* Stone put – for &quot;(1982 Scottish Highland Games Association)&quot; (World Record)
* Braemar Stone throw – for &quot;(1981 World Highland Games)&quot; (World Record)
* Weight throw – over &quot;(1983 Drumtochty Highland Games)&quot;
* Weight over bar – over &quot;(1981 World Highland Games)&quot; (Former World Record)
:→ &quot;Capes held this record for the first time when he cleared at 1981 World&#x27;s Strongest Man&quot;
* Caber toss – for &quot;(1987 Viking Power Challenge)&quot; (Former World Record)
* Scottish hammer throw – for 
* Discus throw – for &quot;(1973)&quot;
